Nigerian on air personality, Mayowa Lambe, has given out a stern warning to any lady who intends to sleep with her husband, Roby Ekpo, expressing that she would be used a surrogate mother. She disclosed this in a video posted via her Instagram page, saying “Any girl that wants to snatch my man because I am not around. “We will just use you and do surrogate for free.” Gani Adams To Nigerians In Diaspora: Shun Negative News, Develop… Jim Iyke Opens Up On Why He Doesn’t Follow Anyone On… The media personality lives overseas, while her husband lives in Nigeria. The couple have been married for six years, and currently do not have any child together.